title: Mapping the Poincaré disk to the half-plane model

The Poincaré disk and half-plane models are related by the map

$$
D^2\to\{\,z\in\C\mid\operatorname{Im} z>0\,\},\quad z\mapsto\frac {z+i} {iz+1}.
$$